     [fee] [dfsdfs] [sfsdfsf]

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Describe in general terms what git-check-with-master does.

=head1 ARGUMENTS

=over 4

=item arg

Describe what arg does, should be, etc. Add a new =item for each distinct arg.

=back

=head1 OPTIONS

=over 4

